**Optional: Per-service .gitignore**

If individual services have unique needs, you can also add service-specific `.gitignore` files:
```
monorepo/
├── .gitignore                    # Root (use the one above)
├── services/
│   ├── auth/
│   │   └── .gitignore           # Service-specific if needed
│   └── orders/
│       └── .gitignore
